          Search Engine Optimization
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg">&#x2022 On-page and technical SEO implementation</p>
        <p class="text-lg">
          &#x2022 Keyword strategy to improve search rankings
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg">
          &#x2022 Drive targeted organic traffic to your site
        </p>
      </ImgContainer>
      <ImgContainer src={img6} href="/services/affiliate-marketing">
        <p class="text-3xl font-semibold hover:text-dd-primary w-fit">
